  "body": "<p>Through my collaboration with <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/creativeoptionscrafts\">Creative Options</a>, I'm not only getting myself more organized (as you can see in <a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/organized-with-creative-options\">yesterday's post</a>), but some other crafty individuals are getting in on the action as well. This time, I called upon four of my favorite crafters to showcase how they put these awesome <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/s/?_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;field-keywords=creative%20options&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;sprefix=creative%20options%2Caps%2C206&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20&amp;url=search-alias%3Darts-crafts&amp;linkId=PG52WT7ABVUOFPEP\">Creative Options products</a> to use.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1597310896732-ESTU64ATY1Q0KAG9GX5Q/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>See how <a href=\"http://www.jengeigley.com/heyjenrenee/2015/8/16/back-to-school-with-creative-options\">Jen</a> and Lotus get ready for Back To School.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1597310921415-XPWCYI69ASJQRD9KDHP6/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Check out how <a href=\"http://www.paigeandchris.com/2015/08/the-one-with-creative-options-back-to.html\">Paige</a> puts some of her favorite crafty supplies in this caddy.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1597310934608-E89Q2N115NL3IP8TY7FT/10c-Creative%2BOptions%2BBack%2BTo%2BSchool.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Love how <a href=\"http://annmarieloves.com/2015/08/18/creative-options/#.VdTqYberzKA\">Ann-Marie</a> mixes in a little creative play with mama time.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1597310959926-E3JU63GP6D77FE0KAX9A/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>And <a href=\"http://delicateconstruction.com/2015/08/the-ultimate-back-to-school-teacher-gift.html\">Michelle Barbour </a>assembled the ultimate teacher gift! She also made this <a href=\"http://delicateconstruction.com/2015/08/diy-school-art-storage-box.html\">school art storage box</a>.</p><p>The products featured can be found at <a href=\"http://www.walmart.com\">Walmart</a> and <a href=\"http://www.hobbylobby.com\">Hobby Lobby</a>.  For crafting tips, giveaways, and product news, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/creativeoptionscrafts\">'Like' Creative Options® on Facebook</a>.</p><p>How are you using Creative Options products? We would love to see, so if you share, use the hashtag #creativeoptions.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
